flowchart LR
  M[master]:::master -->|writes tasks| Q[(headrace — task DAG)]:::board
  Q -->|claim| W[worker]:::worker
  W -->|writes results + learnings| MEM[(Aquifer — memory)]:::board
  W -->|done?| J[judge]:::judge
  J -->|accept: commit| Q
  J -->|reject: retry or block| Q
  MEM -->|find: only relevant slice| M
  MEM --> W
  MEM --> J

  classDef master   fill:#fcecc9,stroke:#c98a1e,color:#3d2700;
  classDef worker   fill:#d7ecf5,stroke:#1b6ca8,color:#082040;
  classDef judge    fill:#f6d9d6,stroke:#b5483d,color:#3d0b08;
  classDef board    fill:#cfeae3,stroke:#1f8a70,color:#0b3020;
